                        <p style="clear:both;"></p>
                        <p><b>Thermo Tech Inc. was founded in 1954. We are a custom manufacturer and your source for flexible connectors, expansion compensators, pipe guides, and rubber, metal or PTFE expansion joints.  We specialize in producing unique products for the food and beverage industry, such as, silicone lined expansion joints/flexible connectors, custom built food grade hoses in several elastomers, and smooth bore PTFE hoses. These products meet or exceed FDA and 3A standards.  We service a multitude of markets including HVAC, plumbing, refrigeration, industrial, hydraulics, oil/gas, water filtration, waste water, food and beverage, breweries, distilleries, wineries, pharmaceutical, pet food, and transportation. Contact us with your piping needs. </b>
